Package: coxdiag
Title: Automated Diagnostics for Cox Proportional Hazards Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chengxi", "Zhou", email = "czhou55@jh.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fits Cox regression models and automatically checks proportional 
    hazards assumptions, generates diagnostic plots, and returns structured summaries.
